{
  "name": "Trailblazer's Torc",
  "type": "equipment",
  "effects": [],
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>The scent of mint and lavender suffuce this bronze necklace. Worn by scouts and explorers of ancient empires, this torc grants you a +1 item bonus to Nature and Stealth checks.</p><hr /><p><strong>Activate - Nature's Aid</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> (concentrate, mental)</p><p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><p><strong>Effect</strong> You @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.GkmbTGfg8KcgynOA]{Create a Diversion} using Nature in place of Deception, calling wildlife to distract your enemies. If you were @UUID[Actor.HyEK1OyIHrV10IRT.Item.u4D6XaWQSBGTDE1M]{Undetected} before this action, you remain undetected.</p><hr /><p>Like all Resonating items, this torc has a slot to fit an aeon stone to it, activating the stone's resonating power and not requiring an additional investment slot. Alongside this, when investing multiple Resonating items, the item gains the following effects.</p><ul><li><p><em>Two Items: </em>The <em>Trailblazer's Torc</em> casts @UUID[Actor.NxVi4ot2bzNOk6Zj.Item.7bh7nji6UEcC5R0s]{Stabilize} on you the first time you recieve the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.yZRUzMqrMmfLu0V1]{Dying} condition per day.</p></li><li><p><em>Three Items: </em>The <em>Trailblazer's Torc</em> allows you to ignore any difficult terrain caused by underbrush or natural growth.</p></li><li><p><em>Four Items: </em>The <em>Trailblazer's Torc's</em> item bonuses increase to +2.</p></li></ul>"
    },
